snippet.title: Valorant Official Console Announcement Gameplay Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2024
snippet.description: VALORANT is a character-based 5v5 tactical shooter set on the global stage. Outwit, outplay, and outshine your competition with tactical abilities, precise gunplay, and adaptive teamwork.
